text: Dora Krsnik (born 19 January 1992) is a Croatian handball player for HBPC and the Croatian national team.EHF profile She participated at the 2016 European Women's Handball Championship.2016 European Championship roster ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian female handball players Category:Sportspeople from Zagreb Category:Expatriate handball players Category:Croatian expatriate sportspeople in Slovenia
